Customizable Tic-Tac-Toe Game
Overview
This is a customizable Tic-Tac-Toe game that allows users to define the grid size (n x n) and the number of consecutive marks (m) required to win. The game is implemented with a clean and intuitive user interface and is responsive across different devices.

Features
Customizable grid size from 3x3 to 10x10.
Customizable win streak length from 3 to the grid size.
Interactive UI for a seamless gaming experience.
Responsive design to work well on both desktop and mobile devices.
Live Demo
You can play the game online at: Live Demo Link

